con:part.con:content: <definitions name="UserDetails" targetNamespace="urn:www.scalaws.org:UserDetails:v1" xmlns="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/wsdl/" xmlns:tns="urn:www.scalaws.org:UserDetails:v1" xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/wsdl/soap/" xmlns:plnk="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2003/05/partner-link/"> <types> <schema targetNamespace="urn:www.scalaws.org:UserDetails:v1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"> <include schemaLocation="UserDetails.xsd"/> </schema> </types> <message name="FindUsersRequestMessage"> <part name="payload" element="tns:FindUsersRequest"/> </message> <message name="FindUsersResponseMessage"> <part name="payload" element="tns:Users"/> </message> <message name="InsertUserRequestMessage"> <part name="payload" element="tns:User"/> </message> <message name="InsertUserResponseMessage"> <part name="payload" element="tns:Done"/> </message> <portType name="UserDetails"> <operation name="findUsers"> <input message="tns:FindUsersRequestMessage"/> <output message="tns:FindUsersResponseMessage"/> </operation> <operation name="insertUser"> <input message="tns:InsertUserRequestMessage"/> <output message="tns:InsertUserResponseMessage"/> </operation> </portType> <binding name="UserDetailsBinding" type="tns:UserDetails"> <soap:binding style="document" transport="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/http"/> <operation name="findUsers"> <soap:operation style="document" soapAction="findUsers"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> <output> <soap:body use="literal"/> </output> </operation> <operation name="insertUser"> <soap:operation style="document" soapAction="insertUser"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> <output> <soap:body use="literal"/> </output> </operation> </binding> <service name="UserDetails"> <port name="UserDetailsPort" binding="tns:UserDetailsBinding"> <soap:address location="http://localhost:9090/services/UserDetails"/> </port> </service> </definitions>
